Scarlett Johansson and Her Rough Night Co-Stars Imagine Your Favorite Celebs as Strippers

Not every exotic dancer’s stage name comes from a combination of their first pet and street they lived on! Case in point: The hilarious pseudonyms the cast of Rough Night gave Hollywood…
